3341//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3342void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_dinf_dref_alis()
3343{
3344 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Alias"); //bit 0 = external/internal data
3345
3346 //Often empty
3347 bool IsInternal;
3348 Get_Flags (Flags, 0, IsInternal, "IsInternal");
3349 if (IsInternal)
3350 return; //Internal stream, no alias
3351
3352 //Parsing
3353 Ztring file_name_string, volume_name_string, Directory_Name;
3354 int16u record_size, record_version, alias_kind;
3355 int8u volume_name_string_length, file_name_string_length;
3356 Element_Begin1("Mac OS Alias Record");
3357 Skip_B4( "user type name/app creator code");
3358 Get_B2 (record_size, "record size");
3359 Get_B2 (record_version, "record version");
3360 if (record_version!=2)
3361 {
3362 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "unknown");
3363 return;
3364 }
3365 int64u End=Element_Offset-8+record_size;
3366 if (End>Element_Size)
3367 End=Element_Size; //Found one file having record_size = the size of the atom, header included
3368 Get_B2 (alias_kind, "alias kind"); Param_Info1(alias_kind?"directory":"file");
3369 Get_B1 (volume_name_string_length, "volume name string length");
3370 if (volume_name_string_length>27)
3371 volume_name_string_length=27;
3372 Get_Local(volume_name_string_length, volume_name_string, "volume name string");
3373 if (volume_name_string_length<27)
3374 Skip_XX(27-volume_name_string_length, "volume name string padding");
3375 Skip_B4( "volume created mac local date"); //seconds since beginning 1904 to 2040
3376 Skip_B2( "file system type");
3377 Skip_B2( "drive type");
3378 Skip_B4( "parent directory ID");
3379 Get_B1 (file_name_string_length, "file name string length");
3380 if (file_name_string_length>99)
3381 file_name_string_length=99;
3382 Get_Local(file_name_string_length, file_name_string, "file name string");
3383 if (file_name_string_length<63)
3384 Skip_XX(63-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding");
3385 if (file_name_string_length<=63)
3386 Skip_B4( "file number");
3387 else if (file_name_string_length<67)
3388 Skip_XX(67-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3389 if (file_name_string_length<=67)
3390 Skip_B4( "file created mac local date");
3391 else if (file_name_string_length<71)
3392 Skip_XX(71-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3393 if (file_name_string_length<=71)
3394 Skip_B4( "file type name");
3395 else if (file_name_string_length<75)
3396 Skip_XX(75-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3397 if (file_name_string_length<=75)
3398 Skip_B4( "file creator name");
3399 else if (file_name_string_length<79)
3400 Skip_XX(79-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3401 if (file_name_string_length<=79)
3402 Skip_B2( "next level up from alias");
3403 else if (file_name_string_length<81)
3404 Skip_XX(81-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3405 if (file_name_string_length<=81)
3406 Skip_B2( "next level down to target");
3407 else if (file_name_string_length<83)
3408 Skip_XX(83-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3409 if (file_name_string_length<=83)
3410 Skip_B4( "volume attributes");
3411 else if (file_name_string_length<87)
3412 Skip_XX(87-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3413 if (file_name_string_length<=87)
3414 Skip_B2( "volume file system ID");
3415 else if (file_name_string_length<89)
3416 Skip_XX(89-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3417 if (file_name_string_length<=89)
3418 Skip_XX(10, "Reserved");
3419 else if (file_name_string_length<99)
3420 Skip_XX(99-file_name_string_length, "file name string padding (hack)");
3421 while(Element_Offset<End)
3422 {
3423 Trusted++;
3424 int16u type, size;
3425 Get_B2 (type, "type");
3426 Get_B2 (size, "size");
3427 switch (type)
3428 {
3429 case 0x0000 :
3430 Get_Local(size, Directory_Name, "Directory Name");
3431 break;
3432 case 0x0002 :
3433 Skip_Local(size, "Absolute Path");
3434 break;
3435 case 0xFFFF :
3436 Skip_XX(End-Element_Offset, "Padding");
3437 break;
3438 default :
3439 Skip_Local(size, "Unknown");
3440 }
3441 if (size%2)
3442 Skip_B1( "Padding");
3443 }
3444 Element_End0();
3445
3446 if (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
3447 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Padding");
3448
3449 FILLING_BEGIN();
3450 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].File_Name.empty()) //Priority to "code" version
3451 {
3452 if (!Directory_Name.empty())
3453 {
3454 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].File_Name+=Directory_Name;
3455 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].File_Name+=ZenLib::PathSeparator;
3456 }
3457 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].File_Name+=file_name_string;
3458 }
3459 FILLING_END();
3460}

3634//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3635void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_co64()
3636{
3637 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Chunk offset");
3638
3639 int64u Offset;
3640 int32u Count;
3641 Get_B4 (Count, "Number of entries");
3642
3643 if (Count==0)
3644 return;
3645
3646 std::vector<int64u> &stco=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stco;
3647 stco.resize(Count<FrameCount_MaxPerStream?Count:FrameCount_MaxPerStream);
3648 int64u* stco_Data=&stco[0];
3649
3650 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<Count; Pos++)
3651 {
3652 //Too much slow
3653 /*
3654 Get_B8 (Offset, "Offset");
3655 */
3656
3657 //Faster
3658 if (Element_Offset+8>Element_Size)
3659 break; //Problem
3660 Offset=BigEndian2int64u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset);
3661 Element_Offset+=8;
3662
3663 if (Pos<FrameCount_MaxPerStream)
3664 {
3665 (*stco_Data)=Offset;
3666 stco_Data++;
3667 }
3668 }
3669}

3760//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3761void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stps()
3762{
3763 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Partial Sync Sample");
3764
3765 //Parsing
3766 int32u sample_count;
3767 Get_B4 (sample_count, "sample-count");
3768
3769 int32u Offset=1; //By default, begin at 1
3770 bool stss_PreviouslyEmpty=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.empty();
3771 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<sample_count; Pos++)
3772 {
3773 int32u sample_number;
3774
3775 //Too much slow
3776 /*
3777 Get_B4 (sample_number, "sample-number");
3778 */
3779
3780 //Faster
3781 if (Element_Offset+4>Element_Size)
3782 break; //Problem
3783 sample_number=BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset);
3784 Element_Offset+=4;
3785
3786 //Coherency testing (first frame is 0 or 1)
3787 if (sample_number==0 && Offset)
3788 {
3789 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.size(); Pos++)
3790 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss[Pos]--;
3791 Offset=0;
3792 }
3793
3794 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.push_back(sample_number-Offset);
3795 }
3796 if (!stss_PreviouslyEmpty)
3797 std::sort(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.begin(), Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.end());
3798}

3802{

3809 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<Count; Pos++)
3810 {
3811 //Too much slow
3812 /*
3813 Element_Begin1("Entry", 12);
3814 int32u SampleDescriptionId;
3815 Get_B4 (Stsc.FirstChunk, "First chunk");
3816 Get_B4 (Stsc.SamplesPerChunk, "Samples per chunk");
3817 Get_B4 (SampleDescriptionId, "Sample description ID");
3818 Element_Info1(Stsc.FirstChunk);

3820 Element_Info1(SampleDescriptionId);
3821 Element_End0();
3822 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stsc.push_back(Stsc);

3824

3853//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3854void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_stpp()
3855{
3856 Element_Name("Subtitle (stpp)");
3857
3858 //Parsing
3859 string NameSpace;
3860 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
3861 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
3862 Skip_B2( "Data reference index");
3863 size_t Pos=(size_t)Element_Offset;
3864 while (Pos<Element_Size)
3865 {
3866 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Pos]=='\0')
3867 break;
3868 Pos++;
3869 }
3870 Get_String(Pos+1-Element_Offset, NameSpace, "namespace");
3871 Pos=(size_t)Element_Offset;
3872 while (Pos<Element_Size)
3873 {
3874 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Pos]=='\0')
3875 break;
3876 Pos++;
3877 }
3878 Skip_Local(Pos+1-Element_Offset, "schema_location");
3879 Pos=(size_t)Element_Offset;
3880 while (Pos<Element_Size)
3881 {
3882 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Pos]=='\0')
3883 break;
3884 Pos++;
3885 }
3886 Skip_Local(Pos+1-Element_Offset, "image_mime_type");
3887
3888 FILLING_BEGIN();
3889 CodecID_Fill(__T("stpp"), StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
3890 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Codec), "stpp", Unlimited, true, true);
3891 if (NameSpace.find("smpte-tt")!=string::npos)
3892 {
3893 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Format), "Timed Text", Unlimited, true, true);
3894
3895 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_TIMEDTEXT_YES
3896 File_TimedText* Parser=new File_TimedText;
3897 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
3898 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
3899 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
3900 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
3901 Parser->IsChapter=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsChapter;
3902 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
3903 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
3904 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TIMEDTEXT_YES
3905 }
3906 FILLING_END();
3907}
3908
3909//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3910void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_text()
3911{
3912 Element_Name("Text (Apple)");
3913
3914 //Parsing
3915 int8u TextName_Size;
3916 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
3917 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
3918 Skip_B2( "Data reference index");
3919 Info_B4(Flags, "Display flags");
3920 Skip_Flags(Flags, 1, "Don't auto scale");
3921 Skip_Flags(Flags, 3, "Use movie background color");
3922 Skip_Flags(Flags, 5, "Scroll in");
3923 Skip_Flags(Flags, 6, "Scroll out");
3924 Skip_Flags(Flags, 7, "Horizontal scroll");
3925 Skip_Flags(Flags, 8, "Reverse scroll");
3926 Skip_Flags(Flags, 9, "Continuous scroll");
3927 Skip_Flags(Flags, 12, "Drop shadow");
3928 Skip_Flags(Flags, 13, "Anti-alias");
3929 Skip_Flags(Flags, 14, "Key text");
3930 Skip_B4( "Text justification");
3931 Skip_B2( "Background color (Red)");
3932 Skip_B2( "Background color (Green)");
3933 Skip_B2( "Background color (Blue)");
3934 Element_Begin1("Default text box");
3935 Skip_B2( "top");
3936 Skip_B2( "left");
3937 Skip_B2( "bottom");
3938 Skip_B2( "right");
3939 Element_End0();
3940 Skip_B8( "Reserved");
3941 Skip_B2( "Font number");
3942 Info_B2(FontFace, "Font face");
3943 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 0, "Bold");
3944 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 1, "Italic");
3945 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 2, "Underline");
3946 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 3, "Outline");
3947 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 4, "Shadow");
3948 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 5, "Condense");
3949 Skip_Flags(FontFace, 6, "Extend");
3950 Skip_B1( "Reserved");
3951 Skip_B1( "Reserved"); //Specs say 16-bits, but not in coherency with my test sample
3952 Skip_B2( "Foreground color (Red)");
3953 Skip_B2( "Foreground color (Green)");
3954 Skip_B2( "Foreground color (Blue)");
3955 Get_B1 (TextName_Size, "Text name size");
3956 Skip_Local(TextName_Size, "Text name");
3957
3958 FILLING_BEGIN();
3959 CodecID_Fill(__T("text"), StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
3960 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Codec), "text", Unlimited, true, true);
3961 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Format), "Timed Text", Unlimited, true, true);
3962
3963 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_TIMEDTEXT_YES
3964 File_TimedText* Parser=new File_TimedText;
3965 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
3966 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
3967 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
3968 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
3969 Parser->IsChapter=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsChapter;
3970 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
3971 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
3972 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TIMEDTEXT_YES
3973 FILLING_END();
3974}

3976//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3977void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_tmcd()
3978{
3979 Element_Name("TimeCode");
3980
3981 //Parsing
3982 stream::timecode *tc=new stream::timecode();
3983 int32u TimeCodeFlags;
3984 int8u NumberOfFrames;
3985 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
3986 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
3987 Skip_B2( "Data reference index");
3988 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
3989 Get_B4 (TimeCodeFlags, "Flags (timecode)");
3990 Get_Flags (TimeCodeFlags, 0, tc->DropFrame, "Drop frame");
3991 Get_Flags (TimeCodeFlags, 1, tc->H24, "24 hour max ");
3992 Get_Flags (TimeCodeFlags, 2, tc->NegativeTimes, "Negative times OK");
3993 Skip_Flags(TimeCodeFlags, 3, "Counter");
3994 Get_B4 (tc->TimeScale, "Time scale");
3995 Get_B4 (tc->FrameDuration, "Frame duration");
3996 Get_B1 (NumberOfFrames, "Number of frames");
3997 if (Element_Size==Element_Offset+3 || (Element_Size>=Element_Offset+7 && Element_Size>=Element_Offset+7+BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+3)))
3998 Skip_B3( "Reserved");
3999 else
4000 Skip_B1( "Reserved"); //Non-standard but several files are like that
4001
4002 FILLING_BEGIN();
4003 //Bug in one file
4004 if (tc->TimeScale==25 && tc->FrameDuration==100)
4005 tc->TimeScale=2500;
4006
4007 if (StreamKind_Last!=Stream_Other)
4008 {
4009 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Other);
4010 Fill(Stream_Other, StreamPos_Last, Other_Type, "Time code");
4011 Fill(Stream_Other, StreamPos_Last, Other_Format, "QuickTime TC");
4012 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamKind=Stream_Other;
4013 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
4014 }
4015
4016 //Filling
4017 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].TimeCode=tc;
4018
4019 //Preparing TimeCode parser
4020 File_Mpeg4_TimeCode* Parser=new File_Mpeg4_TimeCode;
4021 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
4022 mdat_Pos_ToParseInPriority_StreamIDs.push_back(moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID);
4023 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsPriorityStream=true;
4024 ((File_Mpeg4_TimeCode*)Parser)->NumberOfFrames=NumberOfFrames; //tc->FrameDuration?(((float64)tc->TimeScale)/tc->FrameDuration):0;
4025 ((File_Mpeg4_TimeCode*)Parser)->DropFrame=tc->DropFrame;
4026 ((File_Mpeg4_TimeCode*)Parser)->NegativeTimes=tc->NegativeTimes;
4027 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4028 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
4029 FILLING_ELSE();
4030 delete tc; //tc=NULL;
4031 FILLING_END();
4032}

4034//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4035void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_tmcd_name()
4036{
4037 Element_Name("Name (TimeCode)");
4038
4039 //Parsing
4040 Ztring Value;
4041 int16u Size, Language;
4042 Get_B2(Size, "Size");
4043 Get_B2(Language, "Language"); Param_Info1(Language_Get(Language));
4044 if (Size)
4045 {
4046 int8u Junk;
4047 Peek_B1(Junk);
4048 if (Junk<0x20)
4049 {
4050 Skip_B1( "Junk");
4051 Size--;
4052 }
4053 }
4054 Get_Local(Size, Value, "Value");
4055
4056 FILLING_BEGIN();
4057 Fill(Stream_Other, StreamPos_Last, "Title", Value);
4058 FILLING_END();
4059}

4069 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
4070 Skip_B2( "Data reference index");

4100 Skip_B2( "bottom");
4101 Skip_B2( "right");

4111 Skip_B1( "text-color-rgba (green)");

4135//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4136void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_tx3g_ftab()
4137{
4138 Element_Name("Font table");
4139
4140 //Found strange data in one file, but no specs about this
4141 if (Element_Size==0x17-8 && (BigEndian2int16u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset)!=1 || BigEndian2int16u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+4)!=0x17-8-5))
4142 {
4143 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown");
4144 return;
4145 }
4146
4147 //Parsing
4148 int16u entry_count;
4149 Get_B2 (entry_count, "entry-count");
4150
4151 for (int16u Pos=0; Pos<entry_count; Pos++)
4152 {
4153 int8u FontName_Length;
4154 Skip_B2( "font-ID");
4155 Get_B1 (FontName_Length, "font-name-length");
4156 Skip_Local(FontName_Length, "font-name");
4157 }
4158}
4159
4160//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4161void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx()
4162{
4163 //Parsing
4164 Skip_B6( "Reserved");
4165 Skip_B2( "Data reference index");
4166
4167 //Test of buggy files
4168 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Other && Element_Code==0x61766331) //"avc1"
4169 {
4170 //Seen 1 file with "avc1" CodecID but with hdlr atom having "hint" subtype, quick and dirty hack
4171 //TODO: something more generic for handling wrong hdlr atom
4172 Stream_Erase(Stream_Other, StreamPos_Last);
4173 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Video);
4174 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamKind=StreamKind_Last;
4175 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
4176 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "WrongSubType", "Yes");
4177 }
4178
4179 //Test of VBI
4180 if (StreamKind_Last == Stream_Video && Element_Code == 0x4F766269) //"Ovbi"
4181 {
4182 Stream_Erase(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last);
4183 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Other);
4184 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamKind = StreamKind_Last;
4185 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamPos = StreamPos_Last;
4186 }
4187
4188 FILLING_BEGIN()
4189 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max)
4190 {
4191 switch (Element_Code)
4192 {
4193 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_mp4a : Stream_Prepare(Stream_Audio); break;
4194 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_mp4v : Stream_Prepare(Stream_Video); break;
4195 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_mp4s : Stream_Prepare(Stream_Other); break;
4196 default : ;
4197 }
4198
4199 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamKind=StreamKind_Last;
4200 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
4201 }
4202
4203 switch (StreamKind_Last)
4204 {
4205 case Stream_Video : moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxVideo(); break;
4206 case Stream_Audio : moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxSound(); break;
4207 case Stream_Text : moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxText (); break;
4208 default :
4209 CodecID_Fill(Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
4210 switch (Element_Code)
4211 {
4212 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_mp4s : moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxStream(); break;
4213 default : Skip_XX(Element_TotalSize_Get()-Element_Offset, "Unknown");
4214 }
4215 }
4216 if (Element_IsWaitingForMoreData())
4217 return;
4218
4219 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size()==1 && !Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "Encryption").empty())
4220 {
4221 Finish(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0]);
4222 }
4223 moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos++;
4224 FILLING_END();
4225}
4226
4227//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4228void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxSound()
4229{
4230 Element_Name("Audio");
4231
4232 int64s SampleRate;
4233 int32u Channels, SampleSize, Flags=0;
4234 int16u Version, ID;
4235 Get_B2 (Version, "Version");
4236 Skip_B2( "Revision level");
4237 Skip_C4( "Vendor");
4238 if (Version<2) // Version 0 or 1
4239 {
4240 int16u Channels16, SampleSize16, SampleRate16;
4241 Get_B2 (Channels16, "Number of channels");
4242 Get_B2 (SampleSize16, "Sample size");
4243 Get_B2 (ID, "Compression ID");
4244 Skip_B2( "Packet size");
4245 Get_B2 (SampleRate16, "Sample rate"); Param_Info2(SampleRate16, " Hz");
4246 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
4247 if (Version>=1)
4248 {
4249 Skip_B4( "Samples per packet");
4250 Skip_B4( "Bytes per packet");
4251 Skip_B4( "Bytes per frame");
4252 Skip_B4( "Bytes per sample");
4253 }
4254 Channels=Channels16;
4255 SampleSize=SampleSize16;
4256 SampleRate=SampleRate16;
4257 }
4258 else if (Version==2)
4259 {
4260 float64 SampleRateF64;
4261 Skip_B2( "Reserved (0x0003)");
4262 Skip_B2( "Reserved (0x0010)");
4263 Skip_B2( "Reserved (0xFFFE)");
4264 Skip_B2( "Reserved (0x0000)");
4265 Skip_B4( "Reserved (0x00010000)");
4266 Skip_B4( "Size of Struct");
4267 Get_BF8(SampleRateF64, "Sample rate");
4268 Get_B4 (Channels, "Number of channels");
4269 Skip_B4( "Reserved (0x7F000000)");
4270 Get_B4 (SampleSize, "Sample size");
4271 Get_B4 (Flags, "Flags");
4272 Skip_B4( "Bytes per packet");
4273 Skip_B4( "Frames per packet");
4274
4275 SampleRate=float64_int64s(SampleRateF64);
4276 }
4277 else
4278 {
4279 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown");
4280 return;
4281 }
4282
4283 //Bug found in one file: sample size is 16 with a 24-bit CodecID ("in24")
4284 if (Element_Code==0x696E3234 && SampleSize==16)
4285 SampleSize=24; //Correcting the header
4286 //Bug found in one file: sample size is 16 with a 32-bit CodecID ("fl32")
4287 if (Element_Code==0x666C3332 && SampleSize==16)
4288 SampleSize=32; //Correcting the header
4289
4290 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos)
4291 return; //Handling only the first description
4292
4293 FILLING_BEGIN();
4294 //samr bug viewed in some files: channels and Sampling rate are wrong
4295 if (Element_Code==0x73616D72) //"samr"
4296 {
4297 SampleRate=8000;
4298 Channels=1;
4299 }
4300
4301 //lpcm puts "1" in the SampleRate field and Timescale is the real sample size
4302 if (Element_Code==0x6C70636D && SampleRate==1) //"lpcm"
4303 {
4304 SampleRate=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].mdhd_TimeScale;
4305 }
4306
4307 std::string Codec;
4308 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0xFF000000)>>24));
4309 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x00FF0000)>>16));
4310 if (Codec!="ms") //Normal
4311 {
4312 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x0000FF00)>> 8));
4313 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x000000FF)>> 0));
4314 if (Codec!="mp4a") //mp4a is for Mpeg4 system
4315 CodecID_Fill(Ztring(Codec.c_str()), Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
4316 if (Codec!="raw ")
4317 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, Codec, false, true);
4318 else
4319 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, "PCM", Error, false, true);
4320 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec_CC, Codec, false, true);
4321 if (Codec=="drms")
4322 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encryption, "iTunes");
4323 if (Codec=="enca")
4324 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encryption, "Encrypted");
4325 }
4326 else //Microsoft 2CC
4327 {
4328 int64u CodecI= ((Element_Code&0x0000FF00ULL)>> 8)
4329 + ((Element_Code&0x000000FFULL)>> 0); //FormatTag
4330 Codec=Ztring().From_Number(CodecI, 16).To_Local();
4331 CodecID_Fill(Ztring::ToZtring(CodecI, 16), Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Riff);
4332 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, Codec, true);
4333 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec_CC, Codec, true);
4334 }
4335 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AAC_YES)
4336 if (Version==2 && Element_Code==Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_mp4a) //This is not normal, but I don't know where is audioObjectType, default to 2 (AAC LC)
4337 {
4338 File_Aac* Parser=new File_Aac;
4339 Parser->AudioSpecificConfig_OutOfBand(SampleRate, 2);
4340 Parser->Mode=File_Aac::Mode_raw_data_block;
4341 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4342 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4343 }
4344 #endif
4345 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AMR_YES)
4346 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("AMR"))
4347 {
4348 //Creating the parser
4349 File_Amr MI;
4350 MI.Codec=Ztring().From_Local(Codec.c_str());
4351 Open_Buffer_Init(&MI);
4352
4353 //Parsing
4354 Open_Buffer_Continue(&MI, 0);
4355
4356 //Filling
4357 Finish(&MI);
4358 Merge(MI, StreamKind_Last, 0, StreamPos_Last);
4359 }
4360 #endif
4361 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_ADPCM_YES)
4362 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("ADPCM"))
4363 {
4364 //Creating the parser
4365 File_Adpcm MI;
4366 MI.Codec=Ztring().From_Local(Codec.c_str());
4367 Open_Buffer_Init(&MI);
4368
4369 //Parsing
4370 Open_Buffer_Continue(&MI, 0);
4371
4372 //Filling
4373 Finish(&MI);
4374 Merge(MI, StreamKind_Last, 0, StreamPos_Last);
4375
4376 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsPcm=true;
4377 }
4378 #endif
4379 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_PCM_YES)
4380 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("PCM"))
4381 {
4382 //Info of stream size
4383 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stsz_Sample_Multiplier=Channels*SampleSize/8;
4384 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4385 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].PtsDtsAreSame=true;
4386 #endif // MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4387
4388 //Creating the parser
4389 if ((Channels==1 && (StreamPos_Last%2)==0)
4390 || (Streams.find(moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1)!=Streams.end() && Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1].IsPcmMono))
4391 {
4392 File_ChannelGrouping* Parser=new File_ChannelGrouping;
4393 if (StreamPos_Last%2 && !Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1].Parsers.empty())
4394 {
4395 Parser->Channel_Pos=1;
4396 Parser->Common=((File_ChannelGrouping*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1].Parsers[0])->Common;
4397 Parser->StreamID=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1;
4398 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID-1;
4399 }
4400 else
4401 {
4402 Parser->Channel_Pos=0;
4403 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsPcmMono=true;
4404 }
4405 Parser->Channel_Total=2;
4406 Parser->SamplingRate=(int16u)SampleRate;
4407 Parser->BitDepth=(int8u)SampleSize;
4408
4409 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4410 }
4411
4412 //Specific cases
4413 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_SMPTEST0337_YES)
4414 if (Channels==2 && SampleSize<=32 && SampleRate==48000) //Some SMPTE ST 337 streams are hidden in PCM stream
4415 {
4416 File_SmpteSt0337* Parser=new File_SmpteSt0337;
4417 Parser->Container_Bits=(int8u)SampleSize;
4418 Parser->Endianness=(Flags&0x02)?'B':'L';
4419 Parser->ShouldContinueParsing=true;
4420 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4421 if (Config->Demux_Unpacketize_Get())
4422 {
4423 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
4424 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
4425 }
4426 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4427 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4428 }
4429 #endif
4430
4431 //PCM parser
4432 File_Pcm* Parser=new File_Pcm;
4433 Parser->Channels=(int8u)Channels;
4434 Parser->SamplingRate=(int32u)SampleRate;
4435 Parser->BitDepth=(int8u)SampleSize;
4436 Parser->Sign='S'; //Default is "Signed" with QuickTime (to be confirmed), may be changed by flags
4437 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4438 if (Config->Demux_Unpacketize_Get())
4439 {
4440 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
4441 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
4442 }
4443 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4444 if (Version==2)
4445 {
4446 if (Flags&0x01)
4447 Parser->Endianness='F';
4448 else
4449 {
4450 Parser->Endianness=(Flags&0x02)?'B':'L';
4451 Parser->Sign=(Flags&0x04)?'S':'U';
4452 }
4453 }
4454 Parser->Codec=Ztring().From_Local(Codec.c_str());
4455 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4456 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsPcm=true;
4457
4458 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4459 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
4460 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4461 }
4462 #endif
4463 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGA_YES)
4464 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("MPEG Audio"))
4465 {
4466 //Creating the parser
4467 File_Mpega* Parser=new File_Mpega;
4468 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4469 }
4470 #endif
4471 if (Element_Code==0x6F776D61) //"owma"
4472 {
4473 //Parsing
4474 int32u SamplingRate, BytesPerSec;
4475 int16u CodecID, Channels, Data_Size, Resolution;
4476 Get_L2 (CodecID, "Codec ID");
4477 Get_L2 (Channels, "Number of Channels");
4478 Get_L4 (SamplingRate, "Samples Per Second");
4479 Get_L4 (BytesPerSec, "Average Number of Bytes Per Second");
4480 Skip_L2( "Block Alignment");
4481 Get_L2 (Resolution, "Bits / Sample");
4482 Get_L2 (Data_Size, "Codec Specific Data Size");
4483
4484 //Filling
4485 Ztring Codec; Codec.From_Number(CodecID, 16);
4486 Codec.MakeUpperCase();
4487 CodecID_Fill(Codec, Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Riff);
4488 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, Codec); //May be replaced by codec parser
4489 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec_CC, Codec);
4490 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels, 10, true);
4491 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate, SamplingRate, 10, true);
4492 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitRate, BytesPerSec*8, 10, true);
4493 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitDepth, Resolution, 10, true);
4494
4495 FILLING_BEGIN();
4496 //Creating the parser
4497 if (0);
4498 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGA_YES)
4499 else if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Riff, Ztring::ToZtring(CodecID, 16))==__T("MPEG Audio"))
4500 {
4501 File_Mpega* Parser=new File_Mpega;
4502 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4503 }
4504 #endif
4505 FILLING_END();
4506
4507 //Parsing
4508 if (Data_Size>0)
4509 {
4510 Element_Begin1("Codec Specific Data");
4511 switch (CodecID)
4512 {
4513 case 0x0161 :
4514 //Parsing
4515 Skip_L4( "SamplesPerBlock");
4516 Skip_L2( "EncodeOptions");
4517 Skip_L4( "SuperBlockAlign");
4518 break;
4519 default : Skip_XX(Data_Size, "Unknown");
4520 }
4521 Element_End0();
4522 }
4523
4524 //Demux
4525 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4526 if (!((MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("AVC") && Config->Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10_Get())
4527 || (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("HEVC") && Config->Demux_Hevc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_AnnexB_Get())))
4528 switch (Config->Demux_InitData_Get())
4529 {
4530 case 0 : //In demux event
4531 Demux_Level=2; //Container
4532 Demux(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset-(18+Data_Size), (size_t)(18+Data_Size), ContentType_Header);
4533 break;
4534 case 1 : //In field
4535 {
4536 std::string Data_Raw((const char*)(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset-(18+Data_Size)), (size_t)(18+Data_Size));
4537 std::string Data_Base64(Base64::encode(Data_Raw));
4538 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, "Demux_InitBytes", Data_Base64);
4539 (*Stream_More)[Stream_Audio][StreamPos_Last](Ztring().From_Local("Demux_InitBytes"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
4540 }
4541 break;
4542 default : ;
4543 }
4544 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4545 }
4546
4547 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4548 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty() && Config_Demux)
4549 {
4550 File__Analyze* Parser=new File__Analyze; //Only for activating Demux
4551 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4552 }
4553 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4554 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size(); Pos++)
4555 {
4556 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
4557 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
4558 Open_Buffer_Init(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos]);
4559 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
4560 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
4561 }
4562
4563 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels, 10, true);
4564 if (SampleSize!=0 && Element_Code!=0x6D703461 && (Element_Code&0xFFFF0000)!=0x6D730000 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitDepth).empty()) //if not mp4a, and not ms*
4565 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitDepth, SampleSize, 10, true);
4566 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate, SampleRate, 10, true);
4567
4568 //Sometimes, more Atoms in this atoms
4569 if (Element_Offset+8<Element_Size)
4570 Element_ThisIsAList();
4571 FILLING_END();
4572}

4574//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4575void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxStream()
4576{
4577 Element_Name("Stream"); //Defined in ISO-IEC 14496-14
4578
4579 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos)
4580 return; //Handling only the first description
4581
4582 FILLING_BEGIN();
4583 //Sometimes, more Atoms in this atoms
4584 if (Element_Offset+8<Element_Size)
4585 Element_ThisIsAList();
4586 FILLING_END();
4587}

4593
4594 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos)

4598 Ztring CodecID; CodecID.From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code);

4615 }
4616 #endif
4617 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_TTML_YES)
4618 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Text, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, CodecID, InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("TTML"))
4619 {
4620 //Creating the parser
4621 File_Ttml* Parser=new File_Ttml;

4633 {
4634 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
4635 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
4636 Open_Buffer_Init(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos]);
4637 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
4638 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
4639 }
4640
4641 //Sometimes, more Atoms in this atoms
4642 if (Element_Offset+8<Element_Size)
4643 Element_ThisIsAList();
4644 FILLING_END();
4645}
4646
4647//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4648void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxxVideo()
4649{
4650 Element_Name("Video");
4651
4652 int16u Width, Height, Depth, ColorTableID;
4653 int8u CompressorName_Size;
4654 bool IsGreyscale;
4655 Skip_B2( "Version");
4656 Skip_B2( "Revision level");
4657 Skip_C4( "Vendor");
4658 Skip_B4( "Temporal quality");
4659 Skip_B4( "Spatial quality");
4660 Get_B2 (Width, "Width");
4661 Get_B2 (Height, "Height");
4662 Skip_B4( "Horizontal resolution");
4663 Skip_B4( "Vertical resolution");
4664 Skip_B4( "Data size");
4665 Skip_B2( "Frame count");
4666 Peek_B1(CompressorName_Size);
4667 if (CompressorName_Size<32)
4668 {
4669 //This is pascal string
4670 Skip_B1( "Compressor name size");
4671 Skip_Local(CompressorName_Size, "Compressor name");
4672 Skip_XX(32-1-CompressorName_Size, "Padding");
4673 }
4674 else
4675 //this is hard-coded 32-byte string
4676 Skip_Local(32, "Compressor name");
4677 Get_B2 (Depth, "Depth");
4678 if (Depth>0x20 && Depth<0x40)
4679 {
4680 Depth-=0x20;
4681 IsGreyscale=true;
4682 }
4683 else if (Depth==1)
4684 IsGreyscale=true;
4685 else
4686 IsGreyscale=false;
4687 Get_B2 (ColorTableID, "Color table ID");
4688 if (!IsGreyscale && (Depth>1 && Depth<=8) && !ColorTableID)
4689 {
4690 int32u ColorStart;
4691 int16u ColorEnd;
4692 Get_B4 (ColorStart, "Color Start");
4693 Skip_B2( "Color Count");
4694 Get_B2 (ColorEnd, "Color End");
4695 for (int32u Color=ColorStart; Color<=ColorEnd; Color++)
4696 {
4697 Skip_B2( "Alpha");
4698 Skip_B2( "Red");
4699 Skip_B2( "Green");
4700 Skip_B2( "Blue");
4701 }
4702 }
4703
4704 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos)
4705 return; //Handling only the first description
4706
4707 FILLING_BEGIN();
4708 std::string Codec;
4709 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0xFF000000)>>24));
4710 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x00FF0000)>>16));
4711 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x0000FF00)>> 8));
4712 Codec.append(1, (char)((Element_Code&0x000000FF)>> 0));
4713 if (Codec!="mp4v") //mp4v is for Mpeg4 system
4714 CodecID_Fill(Ztring(Codec.c_str()), Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
4715 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Codec, Codec, false, true);
4716 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Codec_CC, Codec, false, true);
4717 if (Codec=="drms")
4718 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encryption, "iTunes");
4719 if (Codec=="encv")
4720 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encryption, "Encrypted");
4721 if (Width)
4722 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Width, Width, 10, true);
4723 if (Height)
4724 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Height, Height, 10, true);
4725 if (moov_trak_tkhd_DisplayAspectRatio && Height && moov_trak_tkhd_DisplayAspectRatio!=((float32)Width)/Height)
4726 {
4727 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, moov_trak_tkhd_DisplayAspectRatio, 3, true);
4728 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_PixelAspectRatio, moov_trak_tkhd_DisplayAspectRatio/Width*Height, 3, true);
4729 }
4730 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Rotation, moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation, 3);
4731 if (moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation)
4732 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Rotation_String, Ztring::ToZtring(moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation, 0)+__T("\xB0")); //degree sign
4733
4734 //Specific cases
4735 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty())
4736 {
4737 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_YES)
4738 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("DV"))
4739 {
4740 File_DvDif* Parser=new File_DvDif;
4741 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4742 }
4743 #endif
4744 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MXF_YES)
4745 if (Element_Code==0x6D78336E || Element_Code==0x6D783370 || Element_Code==0x6D78356E || Element_Code==0x6D783570) //mx3n, mx3p, mx5n, mx5p
4746 {
4747 File_Mxf* Parser=new File_Mxf;
4748 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser); // Note: MXF parser is set first but MPEG Video parser is still active because some IMX files have no MXF header
4749
4750 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4751 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
4752 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4753 }
4754 #endif
4755 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AIC_YES)
4756 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("AIC"))
4757 {
4758 File_Aic* Parser=new File_Aic;
4759 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4760 }
4761 #endif
4762 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_AVC_YES)
4763 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("AVC"))
4764 {
4765 File_Avc* Parser=new File_Avc;
4766 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4767 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4768 switch ((int32u)Element_Code)
4769 {
4770 case 0x61693132: //ai12
4771 case 0x61693232: //ai22
4772 case 0x61693133: //ai13
4773 case 0x61693233: //ai23
4774 case 0x61693135: //ai15
4775 case 0x61693235: //ai25
4776 case 0x61693236: //ai26
4777 case 0x61693136: //ai16
4778 case 0x61693270: //ai2p
4779 case 0x61693170: //ai1p
4780 case 0x61693171: //ai1q
4781 case 0x61693271: //ai2q
4782 case 0x61693532: //ai52
4783 case 0x61693533: //ai53
4784 case 0x61693535: //ai55
4785 case 0x61693536: //ai56
4786 case 0x61693570: //ai5p
4787 case 0x61693571: //ai5q
4788 case 0x4156696E: //AVin
4789 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level|=(1<<7); //Add the flag, SPS/PPS must be sent
4790 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].CodecID=((int32u)Element_Code);
4791 switch ((Element_Code>>8)&0xF)
4792 {
4793 case 1 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "AVC-Intra 100"); break;
4794 case 2 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "AVC-Intra 200"); break;
4795 case 5 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "AVC-Intra 50"); break;
4796 default: Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny, "AVC-Intra"); break;
4797 }
4798 break;
4799 default :
4800 if (Config->Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10_Get())
4801 {
4802 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
4803 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
4804 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
4805 }
4806 }
4807 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4808 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4809 }
4810 #endif
4811 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_FFV1_YES)
4812 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("FFV1"))
4813 {
4814 File_Ffv1* Parser=new File_Ffv1;
4815 Parser->Width=moov_trak_tkhd_Width;
4816 Parser->Height=moov_trak_tkhd_Height;
4817 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4818 }
4819 #endif
4820 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_H263_YES)
4821 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("H.263"))
4822 {
4823 File_H263* Parser=new File_H263;
4824 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4825 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4826 }
4827 #endif
4828 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_HEVC_YES)
4829 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("HEVC"))
4830 {
4831 File_Hevc* Parser=new File_Hevc;
4832 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4833 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4834 if (Config->Demux_Hevc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_AnnexB_Get())
4835 {
4836 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
4837 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
4838 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
4839 }
4840 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4841 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4842 }
4843 #endif
4844 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGV_YES)
4845 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("MPEG Video"))
4846 {
4847 File_Mpegv* Parser=new File_Mpegv;
4848 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4849 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
4850 Parser->InitDataNotRepeated_Optional=true;
4851 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
4852 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4853 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level==4) //Intermediate
4854 {
4855 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
4856 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
4857 }
4858 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4859 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4860 }
4861 #endif
4862 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_PRORES_YES)
4863 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("ProRes"))
4864 {
4865 File_ProRes* Parser=new File_ProRes;
4866 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4867 }
4868 #endif
4869 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
4870 if (Element_Code!=0x76632D31 && MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("VC-1")) // If "vc-1" CodecID, there is a dvc1 atom, not using the hack with Sequence Header direct search
4871 {
4872 File_Vc1* Parser=new File_Vc1;
4873 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
4874 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
4875 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
4876 Element_Offset=Element_Size;
4877 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4878 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
4879 }
4880 #endif
4881 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_VC3_YES)
4882 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring().From_CC4((int32u)Element_Code), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("VC-3"))
4883 {
4884 File_Vc3* Parser=new File_Vc3;
4885 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4886 }
4887 #endif
4888 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_JPEG_YES)
4889 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("JPEG"))
4890 {
4891 File_Jpeg* Parser=new File_Jpeg;
4892 Parser->StreamKind=Stream_Video;
4893 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4894 }
4895 #endif
4896 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEG4_YES)
4897 if (MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Video, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Ztring(Codec.c_str()), InfoCodecID_Format)==__T("JPEG 2000"))
4898 {
4899 File_Mpeg4* Parser=new File_Mpeg4;
4900 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4901
4902 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4903 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
4904 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4905 }
4906 #endif
4907
4908 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4909 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty() && Config_Demux)
4910 {
4911 File__Analyze* Parser=new File__Analyze; //Only for activating Demux
4912 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
4913 }
4914 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
4915 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size(); Pos++)
4916 if (!Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos]->Status[IsAccepted])
4917 {
4918 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
4919 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
4920 Open_Buffer_Init(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos]);
4921 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
4922 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
4923 }
4924 }
4925
4926 //RGB(A)
4927 if (Codec=="raw " || Codec=="rle ")
4928 {
4929 if (IsGreyscale)
4930 {
4931 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ColorSpace, "Y", Unlimited, true, true);
4932 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_BitDepth, Depth);
4933 }
4934 else if (Depth==32)
4935 {
4936 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ColorSpace, "RGBA", Unlimited, true, true);
4937 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_BitDepth, Depth/4);
4938 }
4939 else
4940 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_BitDepth, Depth/3);
4941 }
4942 else if (Codec=="AVrp")
4943 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_BitDepth, 10);
4944
4945 //Descriptors or a list (we can see both!)
4946 if (Element_Offset+8<=Element_Size
4947 && ((CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+0)>='A' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+0)<='z') || (CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+0)>='0' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+0)<='9'))
4948 && ((CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+1)>='A' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+1)<='z') || (CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+1)>='0' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+1)<='9'))
4949 && ((CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+2)>='A' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+2)<='z') || (CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+2)>='0' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+2)<='9'))
4950 && ((CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+3)>='A' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+3)<='z') || (CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+3)>='0' && CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset+4+3)<='9')))
4951 Element_ThisIsAList();
4952 else if (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
4953 Descriptors();
4954 FILLING_END();
4955}
4956
4957//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4958// Source: http://wiki.multimedia.cx/index.php?title=Apple_Lossless_Audio_Coding
4959void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_alac()
4960{
4961 Element_Name("ALAC");
4962
4963 //Parsing
4964 int32u bitrate, samplerate;
4965 int8u sample_size, channels;
4966 Skip_B4( "?");
4967 Skip_B4( "max sample per frame");
4968 Skip_B1( "?");
4969 Get_B1 (sample_size, "sample size");
4970 Skip_B1( "rice history mult");
4971 Skip_B1( "rice initial history");
4972 Skip_B1( "rice kmodifier");
4973 Get_B1 (channels, "channels");
4974 Skip_B1( "?");
4975 Skip_B1( "?");
4976 Skip_B4( "max coded frame size");
4977 Get_B4 (bitrate, "bitrate");
4978 Get_B4 (samplerate, "samplerate");
4979
4980 FILLING_BEGIN_PRECISE();
4981 if (sample_size)
4982 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitDepth, sample_size, 10, true);
4983 if (channels)
4984 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, channels, 10, true);
4985 if (bitrate)
4986 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitRate_Nominal, bitrate, 10, true);
4987 if (samplerate)
4988 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate, samplerate, 10, true);
4989 FILLING_END();
4990}

5031//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5032void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_ARES()
5033{
5034 Element_Name("Avid Resolution Coding Type");
5035
5036 //Parsing
5037 //Source: http://lists.apple.com/archives/quicktime-api/2012/Mar/msg00039.html
5038 int32u x1;
5039 Skip_C4( "Tag");
5040 Skip_C4( "Version");
5041 Skip_B4( "Compression ID"); //Compression ID, From inspection this is 160 for MPEG 50, 161 for MPEG 40 and 162 for MPEG 30. 171 for raw?
5042 Skip_B4( "Field width");
5043 Skip_B4( "Field height");
5044 Get_B4 (x1, "Number of fields"); Param_Info1(x1==1?"Progressive":x1==2?"Interlaced":"");
5045 Skip_B4( "Number of black lines");
5046 Skip_B4( "Video format"); // 1 = NTSC, 2 = PAL, 3 = Custom, 4 = 1080i, 5 = 1080p, 6 = 720p
5047 Skip_B4( "Compression table ID");
5048 Skip_B4( "Render min scale factor (part 1)");
5049 Skip_B4( "Render min scale factor (part 2)");
5050 Skip_B4( "Render min scale factor (part 3)");
5051 Skip_String(32, "Name");
5052 Skip_String(32, "Format");
5053
5054 switch (x1)
5055 {
5056 case 0x01 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType, "Progressive", Unlimited, true, true); break;
5057 case 0x02 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced", Unlimited, true, true); break;
5058 default : ;
5059 }
5060}

5069 Skip_C4( "Version");
5070 Skip_B4( "Field structure ordering"); // 1 = Split fields, 2 = Interlaced fields
5071 Skip_B4( "Field time ordering"); // 1 = First field in buffer is odd (timecode 1), 2 = First field in buffer is even (timecode 2)
5072 Skip_B4( "Field display ordering"); // 1 = First field in time display first line, 2 = First field in time display second line,
5073 Skip_B4( "Byte ordering"); // 1 = YCbCr, 2 = CbYCrY
5074 Skip_B4( "Reserved"); // Must be 0

5077//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5078void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_avcC()
5079{
5080 Element_Name("AVC decode");
5081
5082 //Parsing
5083 int8u Version;
5084 Get_B1 (Version, "Version");
5085 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5086 {
5087 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data not analyzed");
5088 return; //Handling only the first description
5089 }
5090 else if (Version==1)
5091 {
5092 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_AVC_YES
5093 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size(); Pos++) //Removing any previous parser (in case of multiple streams in one track, or dummy parser for demux)
5094 delete Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos];
5095 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.clear();
5096
5097 File_Avc* Parser=new File_Avc;
5098 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
5099 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5100 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID;
5101 if (Config->Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10_Get())
5102 {
5103 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
5104 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
5105 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
5106 }
5107 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5108 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5109 Parser->MustParse_SPS_PPS=true;
5110 Parser->MustSynchronize=false;
5111 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5112 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5113
5114 //Demux
5115 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5116 if (!Config->Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10_Get())
5117 switch (Config->Demux_InitData_Get())
5118 {
5119 case 0 : //In demux event
5120 Demux_Level=2; //Container
5121 Demux(Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size, ContentType_Header);
5122 break;
5123 case 1 : //In field
5124 {
5125 std::string Data_Raw((const char*)(Buffer+Buffer_Offset), (size_t)Element_Size);
5126 std::string Data_Base64(Base64::encode(Data_Raw));
5127 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "Demux_InitBytes", Data_Base64);
5128 (*Stream_More)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_Last](Ztring().From_Local("Demux_InitBytes"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
5129 }
5130 break;
5131 default : ;
5132 }
5133 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5134
5135 //Parsing
5136 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5137
5138 Parser->MustParse_SPS_PPS=false;
5139 Parser->SizedBlocks=true; //Now this is SizeBlocks
5140 #else
5141 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "AVC Data");
5142 #endif
5143 }
5144 else
5145 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Data");
5146}

5191//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5192void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_chan()
5193{
5194 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Channels");
5195
5196 //Parsing
5197 //From http://developer.apple.com/mac/library/documentation/MusicAudio/Reference/CAFSpec/CAF_spec/CAF_spec.html
5198 std::string ChannelDescription_Layout;
5199 int64u ChannelLabels=0;
5200 int32u ChannelLayoutTag, ChannelBitmap, NumberChannelDescriptions;
5201 bool ChannelLabels_Valid=true;
5202 Get_B4 (ChannelLayoutTag, "ChannelLayoutTag");
5203 Get_B4 (ChannelBitmap, "ChannelBitmap");
5204 Get_B4 (NumberChannelDescriptions, "NumberChannelDescriptions");
5205 if (ChannelLayoutTag==0) //UseChannelDescriptions
5206 {
5207 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<NumberChannelDescriptions; Pos++)
5208 {
5209 int32u ChannelLabel;
5210 Get_B4 (ChannelLabel, "ChannelLabel");
5211 if (ChannelLabel<64)
5212 ChannelLabels|=(((int64u)1)<<ChannelLabel);
5213 else
5214 ChannelLabels_Valid=false;
5215 ChannelDescription_Layout+=Mpeg4_chan_ChannelDescription_Layout(ChannelLabel);
5216 ChannelDescription_Layout+=__T(' ');
5217 Skip_B4( "ChannelFlags");
5218 Skip_BF4( "Coordinates (0)");
5219 Skip_BF4( "Coordinates (1)");
5220 Skip_BF4( "Coordinates (2)");
5221 }
5222 if (!ChannelDescription_Layout.empty())
5223 ChannelDescription_Layout.resize(ChannelDescription_Layout.size()-1);
5224 }
5225
5226 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5227 return; //Handling only the first description
5228
5229 FILLING_BEGIN();
5230 if (ChannelLayoutTag==0) //UseChannelDescriptions
5231 {
5232 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelLayout, ChannelDescription_Layout.c_str(), Unlimited, true, true);
5233 if (ChannelLabels_Valid)
5234 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelPositions, Mpeg4_chan_ChannelDescription(ChannelLabels), true, true);
5235 else
5236 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelPositions, ChannelDescription_Layout);
5237 }
5238 else if (ChannelLayoutTag==0x10000) //UseChannelBitmap
5239 {
5240 int8u Channels=0;
5241 for (size_t Bit=0; Bit<18; Bit++)
5242 if (ChannelBitmap&(1<<Bit))
5243 {
5244 Channels++;
5245 ChannelDescription_Layout+=Mpeg4_chan_ChannelBitmap_Layout((int32u)(Bit));
5246 ChannelDescription_Layout+=__T(' ');
5247 }
5248 if (Channels)
5249 {
5250 //Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels, 10, true); //Channel count from this atom should not be used as a primary source, it may be wrong
5251 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelPositions, Mpeg4_chan_ChannelBitmap(ChannelBitmap), true, true);
5252 if (!ChannelDescription_Layout.empty())
5253 {
5254 ChannelDescription_Layout.resize(ChannelDescription_Layout.size()-1);
5255 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelLayout, ChannelDescription_Layout.c_str(), Unlimited, true, true);
5256 }
5257 }
5258 }
5259 else if (ChannelLayoutTag>0x10000)
5260 {
5261 //int16u Channels=ChannelLayoutTag&0x0000FFFF;
5262 int16u Ordering=(ChannelLayoutTag&0xFFFF0000)>>16;
5263 //Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels, 10, true); //Channel count from this atom should not be used as a primary source, it may be wrong
5264 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelPositions, Mpeg4_chan(Ordering), Unlimited, true, true);
5265 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_ChannelLayout, Mpeg4_chan_Layout(Ordering));
5266 }
5267 FILLING_END();
5268}

5298//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5299void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr()
5300{
5301 Element_Name("Color Parameter");
5302
5303 //Parsing
5304 int32u ColorParameterType;
5305 Get_C4 (ColorParameterType, "Color parameter type");
5306 switch (ColorParameterType)
5307 {
5308 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_clcn: moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_nclc(true); break;
5309 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_nclc: moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_nclc(); break;
5310 case Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_prof: moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_prof(); break;
5311 default : Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Unknown");

5315//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5316void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_colr_nclc(bool LittleEndian)
5317{
5318 //Parsing
5319 int16u colour_primaries, transfer_characteristics, matrix_coefficients;
5320 if (LittleEndian)
5321 Get_L2 (colour_primaries, "Primaries index");
5322 else
5323 Get_B2 (colour_primaries, "Primaries index");
5324 Param_Info1(Mpegv_colour_primaries((int8u)colour_primaries));
5325 if (LittleEndian)
5326 Get_L2 (transfer_characteristics, "Transfer function index");
5327 else
5328 Get_B2 (transfer_characteristics, "Transfer function index");
5329 Param_Info1(Mpegv_transfer_characteristics((int8u)transfer_characteristics));
5330 if (LittleEndian)
5331 Get_L2 (matrix_coefficients, "Matrix index");
5332 else
5333 Get_B2 (matrix_coefficients, "Matrix index");
5334 Param_Info1(Mpegv_matrix_coefficients((int8u)matrix_coefficients));
5335
5336 FILLING_BEGIN();
5337 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_colour_description_present).empty()) //Using only the first one met
5338 {
5339 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_colour_description_present, "Yes");
5340 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_colour_primaries, Mpegv_colour_primaries((int8u)colour_primaries));
5341 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_transfer_characteristics, Mpegv_transfer_characteristics((int8u)transfer_characteristics));
5342 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_matrix_coefficients, Mpegv_matrix_coefficients((int8u)matrix_coefficients));
5343 }
5344 FILLING_END();
5345}

5354//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5355void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_d263()
5356{
5357 Element_Name("H263SpecificBox");
5358
5359 //Parsing
5360 int32u Vendor;
5361 int8u Version, H263_Level, H263_Profile;
5362 Get_C4 (Vendor, "Encoder vendor");
5363 Get_B1 (Version, "Encoder version");
5364 Get_B1 (H263_Level, "H263_Level");
5365 Get_B1 (H263_Profile, "H263_Profile");
5366
5367 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5368 return; //Handling only the first description
5369
5370 Ztring ProfileLevel;
5371 switch (H263_Profile)
5372 {
5373 case 0x00 : ProfileLevel=__T("BaseLine"); break;
5374 default : ProfileLevel.From_Number(H263_Profile);
5375 }
5376 ProfileLevel+=__T('@');
5377 ProfileLevel+=Ztring::ToZtring(((float32)H263_Level)/10, 1);
5378 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Profile, ProfileLevel);
5379 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library_Name, Mpeg4_Vendor(Vendor));
5380 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library_Version, Version);
5381 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library, Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library_Name)+__T(' ')+Ztring::ToZtring(Version));
5382 Ztring Encoded_Library_String=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library_Name)+(Version?(__T(" Revision ")+Ztring::ToZtring(Version)):Ztring());
5383 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Encoded_Library_String, Encoded_Library_String, true);
5384}

5386//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5387void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_dac3()
5388{
5389 Element_Name("AC3SpecificBox");
5390 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, "", Unlimited, true, true); //Remove the value (is always wrong in the stsd atom)
5391
5392 //Parsing
5393 if (Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID)==__T("sac3"))
5394 {
5395 Element_Info1("Nero specific");
5396 int8u Version;
5397 Get_B1 (Version, "Version");
5398 if (Version==1)
5399 {
5400 int8u bsid;
5401 Get_B1 (bsid, "bsid");
5402 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "unknown");
5403 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_AC3_YES
5404 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty())
5405 {
5406 File_Ac3* Parser=new File_Ac3;
5407 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5408 Parser->Frame_Count_Valid=2;
5409 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5410 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5411 }
5412 #else
5413 if (bsid<=0x08)
5414 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamKind_Last, Audio_Format, "AC-3");
5415 if (bsid>0x0A && bsid<=0x10)
5416 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamKind_Last, Audio_Format, "E-AC-3");
5417 #endif
5418 return;
5419 }
5420 else
5421 {
5422 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Data");
5423 return;
5424 }
5425 }
5426
5427 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5428 return; //Handling only the first description
5429
5430 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_AC3_YES
5431 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty())
5432 {
5433 File_Ac3* Parser=new File_Ac3;
5434 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5435 Parser->MustParse_dac3=true;
5436 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5437 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5438
5439 //Parsing
5440 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5441 }
5442 #else
5443 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "AC-3 Data");
5444
5445 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamKind_Last, Audio_Format, "AC-3");
5446 #endif
5447}

5449//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5450void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_damr()
5451{
5452 Element_Name("AMR decode config");
5453
5454 //Parsing
5455 int32u Vendor;
5456 int8u Version;
5457 Get_C4 (Vendor, "Encoder vendor");
5458 Get_B1 (Version, "Encoder version");
5459 Skip_B2( "Packet modes");
5460 Skip_B1( "Number of packet mode changes");
5461 Skip_B1( "Samples per packet");
5462
5463 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5464 return; //Handling only the first description
5465
5466 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name, Mpeg4_Vendor(Vendor));
5467 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Version, Version);
5468 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library, Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name)+__T(' ')+Ztring::ToZtring(Version));
5469 Ztring Encoded_Library_String=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name)+(Version?(__T(" Revision ")+Ztring::ToZtring(Version)):Ztring());
5470 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_String, Encoded_Library_String, true);
5471}

5473//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5474void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_dec3()
5475{
5476 Element_Name("EAC3SpecificBox");
5477 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, "", Unlimited, true, true); //Remove the value (is always wrong in the stsd atom)
5478
5479 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5480 {
5481 return; //Handling only the first description
5482 }
5483
5484 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_AC3_YES
5485 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5486 {
5487 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Data not analyzed");
5488 return; //Handling only the first description
5489 }
5490
5491 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.empty())
5492 {
5493 File_Ac3* Parser=new File_Ac3;
5494 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5495 Parser->Frame_Count_Valid=2;
5496 Parser->MustParse_dec3=true;
5497 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5498 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5499
5500 //Parsing
5501 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5502 }
5503 #else
5504 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "E-AC-3 Data");
5505
5506 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamKind_Last, Audio_Format, "E-AC-3");
5507 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamKind_Last, Audio_Format, "", Unlimited, true, true); //Remove the value (is always wrong in the stsd atom)
5508 #endif

5511//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5512void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_ddts()
5513{
5514 Element_Name("DTSSpecificBox");
5515 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, "", Unlimited, true, true); //Remove the value (is always wrong in the stsd atom)
5516
5517 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5518 {
5519 return; //Handling only the first description
5520 }
5521
5522 //Comments about the new CodecIDs having this atom:
5523 //dtsc: DTS Core only
5524 //dtse: DTS Express, not having DTS Core
5525 //dtsh: DTS Core + DTS Lossless (MA), mixed
5526 //dtsl: DTS Lossless (MA), not having DTS Core
5527
5528 int32u DTSSamplingFrequency, maxBitrate, avgBitrate;
5529 int16u ChannelLayout;
5530 int8u CoreLayout;
5531
5532 //Parsing
5533 Get_B4 (DTSSamplingFrequency, "DTSSamplingFrequency");
5534 Get_B4 (maxBitrate, "maxBitrate");
5535 Get_B4 (avgBitrate, "avgBitrate");
5536 Skip_B1( "pcmSampleDepth"); // 16 or 24 bits
5537 BS_Begin();
5538 Skip_S1(2, "FrameDuration"); // 0 = 512, 1 = 1024, 2 = 2048, 3 = 4096
5539 Skip_S1(5, "StreamConstruction");
5540 Skip_SB( "CoreLFEPresent"); // 0 = none, 1 = LFE exists
5541 Get_S1 (6, CoreLayout, "CoreLayout");
5542 Skip_S2(14, "CoreSize");
5543 Skip_SB( "StereoDownmix"); // 0 = none, 1 = downmix present
5544 Skip_S1 (3, "RepresentationType");
5545 Get_S2 (16, ChannelLayout, "ChannelLayout");
5546 Skip_SB( "MultiAssetFlag"); // 0 = none, 1 = multiple asset
5547 Skip_SB( "LBRDurationMod"); // 0 = ignore, 1 = Special LBR duration modifier
5548 Skip_S1(6, "reserved");
5549 BS_End();
5550
5551 FILLING_BEGIN();
5552 if (DTSSamplingFrequency)
5553 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate, DTSSamplingFrequency, 10, true); //This is the maximum sampling frequency
5554 if (avgBitrate)
5555 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitRate, avgBitrate);
5556 if (maxBitrate)
5557 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitRate_Maximum, maxBitrate);
5558 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTS_YES)
5559 if (ChannelLayout)
5560 {
5561 Fill(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_ChannelPositions, DTS_HD_SpeakerActivityMask(ChannelLayout).c_str());
5562 Fill(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_ChannelPositions_String2, DTS_HD_SpeakerActivityMask2(ChannelLayout).c_str());
5563 }
5564 if (CoreLayout && CoreLayout<16)
5565 {
5566 Fill(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_ChannelPositions, DTS_ChannelPositions[CoreLayout]);
5567 Fill(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_ChannelPositions_String2, DTS_ChannelPositions2[CoreLayout]);
5568 }
5569 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTS_YES)
5570 FILLING_END();
5571}
5572
5573//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5574void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_dvc1()
5575{
5576 Element_Name("VC1SpecificBox");
5577
5578 // Parsing
5579 int32u hrd_buffer, hrd_rate, framerate=0;
5580 int8u profile, level, frmrtq_pp, bitrtq_pp, dquant, vtransform, overlap, syncmarker, rangered, maxbframes, quantizer, finterpflag, no_interlace, no_multiple_seq, no_multiple_entry, no_slice_code, no_bframe;
5581 bool cbr, loopfilter, multires, fastuvmc, extended_mv;
5582
5583 BS_Begin();
5584 Get_S1 (4, profile, "Profile");
5585 Get_S1 (3, level, "Level");
5586 Skip_SB( "reserved");
5587 BS_End();
5588
5589 switch(profile)
5590 {
5591 case 0 : // Simple Profile
5592 case 4 : // Main Profile
5593 BS_Begin();
5594 Get_S1 (3, level, "Level"); // should be the same as above
5595 Get_SB (cbr, "CBR"); // should be equal to 1 if CBR Mode, 0 otherwhise
5596 Skip_S1(4, "Reserved"); // should be set to 0
5597 BS_End();
5598 Get_B3 (hrd_buffer, "HRD_Buffer"); // Buffer Size of Hypothetical Reference Decoder in ms
5599 Get_B4 (hrd_rate, "HRD_Rate"); // Peak Transmisson Rate of the Hypothetical Reference Decoder in bps
5600 Get_B4 (framerate, "FrameRate"); // Rounded FPS of the track
5601 BS_Begin();
5602 Get_S1 (4, profile, "Profile"); // should be the same as above
5603 Get_S1 (3, frmrtq_pp, "Frmrtq_postproc");
5604 Get_S1 (5, bitrtq_pp, "Bitrtq_postproc");
5605 Get_SB (loopfilter, "Loopfilter");
5606 Skip_SB( "Reserved"); // should be set to 0
5607 Get_SB (multires, "MultiRes");
5608 Skip_SB( "Reserved"); // should be set to 1
5609 Get_SB (fastuvmc, "Fastuvmc");
5610 Get_SB (extended_mv, "Extended_mv");
5611 Get_S1 (2, dquant, "Dquant");
5612 Get_S1 (1, vtransform, "Vtransform");
5613 Skip_SB( "Reserved"); // should be set to 0
5614 Get_S1 (1, overlap, "Overlap");
5615 Get_S1 (1, syncmarker, "Syncmarker");
5616 Get_S1 (1, rangered, "Rangered");
5617 Get_S1 (3, maxbframes, "MaxBFrames"); // should be equal to 0 with SP
5618 Get_S1 (2, quantizer, "Quantizer");
5619 Get_S1 (1, finterpflag, "Finterpflag");
5620 Skip_SB( "Reserved"); // should be set to 1
5621 BS_End();
5622 break;
5623 case 12 : // Advanced Profile
5624 BS_Begin();
5625 Get_S1 (3, level, "Level"); // should be the same as above
5626 Get_SB (cbr, "CBR"); // should be equal to 1 if CBR Mode, 0 otherwhise
5627 Skip_S1(6, "Reserved"); // should be set to 0
5628 Get_S1 (1, no_interlace, "No Interlace"); // should be set to 0 for Interlaced Content
5629 Get_S1 (1, no_multiple_seq, "No Multiple Sequence");
5630 Get_S1 (1, no_multiple_entry, "No Multiple Entry");
5631 Get_S1 (1, no_slice_code, "No Slice Code");
5632 Get_S1 (1, no_bframe, "No BFrame");
5633 Skip_SB( "Reserved");
5634 BS_End();
5635 Get_B4 (framerate, "FrameRate");
5636 Element_Begin1("Sequence HDR");
5637 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
5638 File_Vc1* Parser=new File_Vc1;
5639 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
5640 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5641 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5642 Element_Offset=Element_Size;
5643 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5644 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT*/
5645 #else //defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
5646 Skip_XX(Element_Size - Element_Offset, "VC-1 data");
5647 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
5648 Element_End0();
5649 break;
5650 }
5651
5652 FILLING_BEGIN();
5653 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
5654 Ztring Profile, Level;
5655
5656 switch (profile)
5657 {
5658 case 0 : Profile=__T("Simple"); break;
5659 case 4 : Profile=__T("Main"); break;
5660 case 12 : Profile=__T("Advanced"); break;
5661 default : Profile=__T("");
5662 }
5663 Profile+=__T("@");
5664
5665 if (profile == 0) // Simple Profile
5666 {
5667 switch (level)
5668 {
5669 case 0 : Level=__T("Low"); break;
5670 case 2 : Level=__T("Medium"); break;
5671 default : Level=__T("");
5672 }
5673 }
5674 else if (profile == 4) // Main Profile
5675 {
5676 switch (level)
5677 {
5678 case 0 : Level=__T("Low"); break;
5679 case 2 : Level=__T("Medium"); break;
5680 case 4 : Level=__T("High"); break;
5681 default : Level=__T("");
5682 }
5683 }
5684 else if (profile == 12) // Advanced Profile
5685 {
5686 switch (level)
5687 {
5688 case 0 : Level=__T("L0"); break;
5689 case 1 : Level=__T("L1"); break;
5690 case 2 : Level=__T("L2"); break;
5691 case 3 : Level=__T("L3"); break;
5692 case 4 : Level=__T("L4"); break;
5693 default : Level=__T("");
5694 }
5695 }
5696 Profile+=Level;
5697 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Profile, Profile);
5698 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Codec_Profile, Profile);
5699 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_VC1_YES)
5700 if (framerate && framerate!=(int32u)-1)
5701 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Video_FrameRate, framerate, 3);
5702 FILLING_END();
5703}

5723
5724//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5725void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_fiel()
5726{
5727 //Source: http://developer.apple.com/quicktime/icefloe/dispatch019.html#fiel
5728 //Source: QuickTimeFileFormat2011.pdf:
5729 // 1 – T is displayed earliest, T is stored first in the file.
5730 // 6 – B is displayed earliest, B is stored first in the file.
5731 // 9 – B is displayed earliest, T is stored first in the file.
5732 //14 – T is displayed earliest, B is stored first in the file.
5733 Element_Name("Field/Frame Information");
5734
5735 //Parsing
5736 int8u fields, detail;
5737 Get_B1 (fields, "fields");
5738 Get_B1 (detail, "detail");
5739
5740 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5741 return; //Handling only the first description
5742
5743 FILLING_BEGIN();
5744 switch(fields)
5745 {
5746 case 0x01 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType, "Progressive", Unlimited, true, true); break;
5747 case 0x02 : Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced", Unlimited, true, true);
5748 switch(detail)
5749 {
5750 case 1 : // T is displayed earliest, T is stored first in the file.
5751 case 9 : // B is displayed earliest, T is stored first in the file.
5752 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanOrder, "TFF", Unlimited, true, true);
5753 break;
5754 case 6 : // B is displayed earliest, B is stored first in the file.
5755 case 14 : // T is displayed earliest, B is stored first in the file.
5756 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanOrder, "BFF", Unlimited, true, true);
5757 break;
5758 default : ;
5759 }
5760 // Priorizing https://developer.apple.com/library/mac/technotes/tn2162/_index.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/DTS40013070-CH1-TNTAG10-THE__FIEL__IMAGEDESCRIPTION_EXTENSION__FIELD_FRAME_INFORMATION
5761 /*
5762 switch(detail)
5763 {
5764 case 9 : // B is displayed earliest, T is stored first in the file.
5765 case 14 : // T is displayed earliest, B is stored first in the file.
5766 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].ScanOrder_StoredDisplayedInverted=true;
5767 break;
5768 default : ;
5769 }
5770 */
5771 switch (detail)
5772 {
5773 case 1 : // Separated fields, TFF
5774 case 6 : // Separated fields, BFF
5775 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod_FieldsPerBlock, 2, 10, true);
5776 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "SeparatedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
5777 break;
5778 case 9 : // Interleaved fields, TFF
5779 case 14 : // Interleaved fields, BFF
5780 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "InterleavedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
5781 break;
5782 default : ;
5783 }
5784
5785 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_JPEG_YES
5786 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format)==__T("JPEG") && Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size()==1)
5787 ((File_Jpeg*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Interlaced=true;
5788 #endif //MEDIAINFO_JPEG_YES
5789 break;
5790 default : ;
5791 }
5792 FILLING_END();
5793}
5794
5795//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5796void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_glbl()
5797{
5798 Element_Name("Global");
5799
5800 if (Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_MuxingMode)==__T("MXF"))
5801 {
5802 Clear(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_MuxingMode);
5803 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGV_YES)
5804 File_Mpegv* Parser=new File_Mpegv;
5805 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5806
5807 //Re-init
5808 int64u Elemen_Code_Save=Element_Code;
5809 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID; //Element_Code is use for stream identifier
5810 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5811 Element_Code=Elemen_Code_Save;
5812 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5813
5814 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5815 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGV_YES)
5816
5817 //TODO: demux is not done in this case (2 possibilities: MXF wrapped and it is useless, not MXF wrapped and we may need it but up to now we saw only data in this atom redundant with the raw stream data)
5818 return;
5819 }
5820
5821 //Demux
5822 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5823 Demux_Level=2; //Container
5824 Demux(Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size, ContentType_MainStream);
5825 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5826
5827 //Parsing
5828 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size(); Pos++)
5829 Open_Buffer_OutOfBand(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos], Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size);
5830}
5831
5832//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5833void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_hvcC()
5834{
5835 Element_Name("HEVCDecoderConfigurationRecord");
5836
5837 //Parsing
5838 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_HEVC_YES
5839 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size(); Pos++) //Removing any previous parser (in case of multiple streams in one track, or dummy parser for demux)
5840 delete Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[Pos];
5841 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.clear();
5842
5843 File_Hevc* Parser=new File_Hevc;
5844 Parser->FrameIsAlwaysComplete=true;
5845 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5846 Element_Code=moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID;
5847 if (Config->Demux_Hevc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_AnnexB_Get())
5848 {
5849 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Demux_Level=4; //Intermediate
5850 Parser->Demux_Level=2; //Container
5851 Parser->Demux_UnpacketizeContainer=true;
5852 }
5853 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5854 Open_Buffer_Init(Parser);
5855 Parser->MustParse_VPS_SPS_PPS=true;
5856 Parser->MustSynchronize=false;
5857 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.push_back(Parser);
5858 mdat_MustParse=true; //Data is in MDAT
5859
5860 //Demux
5861 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5862 if (!Config->Demux_Hevc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_AnnexB_Get())
5863 switch (Config->Demux_InitData_Get())
5864 {
5865 case 0 : //In demux event
5866 Demux_Level=2; //Container
5867 Demux(Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size, ContentType_Header);
5868 break;
5869 case 1 : //In field
5870 {
5871 std::string Data_Raw((const char*)(Buffer+Buffer_Offset), (size_t)Element_Size);
5872 std::string Data_Base64(Base64::encode(Data_Raw));
5873 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "Demux_InitBytes", Data_Base64);
5874 (*Stream_More)[Stream_Video][StreamPos_Last](Ztring().From_Local("Demux_InitBytes"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
5875 }
5876 break;
5877 default : ;
5878 }
5879 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
5880
5881 //Parsing
5882 Open_Buffer_Continue(Parser);
5883
5884 Parser->SizedBlocks=true; //Now this is SizeBlocks
5885 #else
5886 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "HEVC Data");
5887 #endif
5888}

5987//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
5988void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_wave_enda()

5993
5994 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
5995 return; //Handling only the first description
5996
5997 FILLING_BEGIN();
5998 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_PCM_YES)
5999 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsPcm)
6000 {
6001 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers.size()==1)
6002 ((File_Pcm*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Endianness=Endianness?'L':'B';

6006 ((File_Pcm*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[1])->Endianness=Endianness?'L':'B';
6007 }

6009 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_PCM_YES)
