6013//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6014void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_wave_frma()
6015{
6016 Element_Name("Data format");
6017
6018 //Parsing
6019 int16u Codec_Peek;
6020 Peek_B2(Codec_Peek);
6021 if (Codec_Peek==0x6D73) //"ms", Microsoft 2CC
6022 {
6023 int16u CodecMS;
6024 Skip_C2( "Codec_MS");
6025 Get_B2 (CodecMS, "CC2");
6026
6027 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
6028 return; //Handling only the first description
6029
6030 FILLING_BEGIN();
6031 Ztring OldFormat=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID);
6032 Ztring NewFormat=Ztring::ToZtring(CodecMS, 16);
6033 if (OldFormat!=NewFormat)
6034 {
6035 Clear(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID);
6036 CodecID_Fill(NewFormat, Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Riff);
6037 }
6038 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, CodecMS, 16, true);
6039 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec_CC, CodecMS, 16, true);
6040 FILLING_END();
6041 }
6042 else
6043 {
6044 int32u Codec;
6045 Get_C4(Codec, "Codec");
6046
6047 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
6048 return; //Handling only the first description
6049
6050 FILLING_BEGIN();
6051 if (Codec!=0x6D703461) //"mp4a"
6052 {
6053 Ztring OldFormat=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID);
6054 Ztring NewFormat=Ztring().From_CC4(Codec);
6055 if (OldFormat!=NewFormat)
6056 {
6057 Clear(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID);
6058 CodecID_Fill(NewFormat, Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
6059 }
6060 }
6061 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec, Ztring().From_CC4(Codec), true);
6062 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Codec_CC, Ztring().From_CC4(Codec), true);
6063 FILLING_END();
6064 }
6065}
6066
6067//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6068void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_wave_samr()
6069{
6070 Element_Name("AMR decode config");
6071
6072 //Parsing
6073 int32u Vendor;
6074 int8u Version;
6075 Get_C4 (Vendor, "Encoder vendor");
6076 Get_B1 (Version, "Encoder version");
6077 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Unknown");
6078
6079 if (moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_Pos>1)
6080 return; //Handling only the first description
6081
6082 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name, Mpeg4_Vendor(Vendor));
6083 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Version, Version);
6084 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library, Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name)+__T(' ')+Ztring::ToZtring(Version));
6085 Ztring Encoded_Library_String=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_Name)+(Version?(__T("Revision")+Ztring::ToZtring(Version)):Ztring());
6086 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Encoded_Library_String, Encoded_Library_String, true);
6087}

6098//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6099void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsd_xxxx_wave_xxxx()
6100{
6101 if ((Element_Code&0x6D730000)!=0x6D730000)
6102 return; //Only msxx format is known
6103
6104 Element_Name("Microsoft Audio");
6105
6106 //Parsing
6107 int32u SamplesPerSec, AvgBytesPerSec;
6108 int16u FormatTag, Channels, BitsPerSample;
6109 Get_L2 (FormatTag, "FormatTag");
6110 Get_L2 (Channels, "Channels");
6111 Get_L4 (SamplesPerSec, "SamplesPerSec");
6112 Get_L4 (AvgBytesPerSec, "AvgBytesPerSec");
6113 Skip_L2( "BlockAlign");
6114 Get_L2 (BitsPerSample, "BitsPerSample");
6115
6116 FILLING_BEGIN();
6117 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_, Channels!=5?Channels:6, 10, true);
6118 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate, SamplesPerSec, 10, true);
6119 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitRate_Nominal, AvgBytesPerSec*8, 10, true);
6120 FILLING_END();
6121
6122 //Options
6123 if (Element_Offset+2>Element_Size)
6124 return; //No options
6125
6126 //Parsing
6127 int16u Option_Size;
6128 Get_L2 (Option_Size, "cbSize");
6129
6130 //Filling
6131 if (Option_Size>0)
6132 {
6133 Skip_XX(Option_Size, "Unknown");
6134 }
6135}

6137//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6138void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsh()
6139{
6140 Element_Name("Shadow Sync Sample");
6141
6142 //Parsing
6143 int32u entry_count;
6144 Get_B4 (entry_count, "entry-count");
6145
6146 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<entry_count; Pos++)
6147 {
6148 Skip_B4( "shadowed-sample-number");
6149 Skip_B4( "sync-sample-number");
6150 }
6151}
6152
6153//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6154void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stss()
6155{
6156 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Sync Sample");
6157
6158 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.clear();
6159
6160 //Parsing
6161 int32u entry_count;
6162 Get_B4 (entry_count, "entry-count");
6163
6164 int32u Offset=1; //By default, begin at 1
6165 bool stss_PreviouslyEmpty=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.empty();
6166 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<entry_count; Pos++)
6167 {
6168 int32u sample_number;
6169
6170 //Too much slow
6171 /*
6172 Get_B4 (sample_number, "sample-number");
6173 */
6174
6175 //Faster
6176 if (Element_Offset+4>Element_Size)
6177 break; //Problem
6178 sample_number=BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset);
6179 Element_Offset+=4;
6180
6181 //Coherency testing (first frame is 0 or 1)
6182 if (sample_number==0 && Offset)
6183 {
6184 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.size(); Pos++)
6185 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss[Pos]--;
6186 Offset=0;
6187 }
6188
6189 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.push_back(sample_number-Offset);
6190 }
6191 if (!stss_PreviouslyEmpty)
6192 std::sort(Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.begin(), Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stss.end());
6193}
6194
6195//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6196void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsz()
6197{
6198 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Sample Size")
6199
6200 Stream=Streams.find(moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID);
6201 int32u Sample_Size, Sample_Count;
6202 int8u FieldSize;
6203 if (Element_Code==Elements::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stsz)
6204 {
6205 Get_B4 (Sample_Size, "Sample Size");
6206 FieldSize=32;
6207 }
6208 else
6209 {
6210 Skip_B3( "Reserved");
6211 Get_B1 (FieldSize, "Field size");
6212 Sample_Size=0;
6213 }
6214 Get_B4 (Sample_Count, "Number of entries");
6215
6216 if (Sample_Size>0)
6217 {
6218 //Detecting wrong stream size with some PCM streams
6219 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Audio)
6220 {
6221 const Ztring &Codec=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_CodecID);
6222 if (Codec==__T("raw ")
6223 || MediaInfoLib::Config.CodecID_Get(Stream_Audio, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4, Codec).find(__T("PCM"))==0
6224 || MediaInfoLib::Config.Codec_Get(Codec, InfoCodec_KindofCodec).find(__T("PCM"))==0)
6225 {
6226 int64u Duration=Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Duration).To_int64u();
6227 int64u Resolution=Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_BitDepth).To_int64u();
6228 int64u SamplingRate=Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_SamplingRate).To_int64u();
6229 int64u Channels=Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Audio_Channel_s_).To_int64u();
6230 int64u Stream_Size_Theory=Duration*Resolution*SamplingRate*Channels/8/1000;
6231 int64u Stream_Size_Real=Sample_Size; Stream_Size_Real*=Sample_Count;
6232 for (int64u Multiplier=1; Multiplier<=32; Multiplier++)
6233 if (Stream_Size_Real*Multiplier>Stream_Size_Theory*0.995 && Stream_Size_Real*Multiplier<Stream_Size_Theory*1.005)
6234 {
6235 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stsz_Sample_Multiplier=Multiplier;
6236 break;
6237 }
6238 }
6239 }
6240
6241 Stream->second.stsz_StreamSize=Sample_Size; Stream->second.stsz_StreamSize*=Sample_Count;
6242 if (Sample_Size==1)
6243 Stream->second.stsz_StreamSize*=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stsz_Sample_Multiplier;
6244 else
6245 Stream->second.stsz_Sample_Multiplier=1; //Sampe_Size is correct, no need of stsz_Sample_Multiplier
6246
6247 Stream->second.stsz_Sample_Size=Sample_Size;
6248 Stream->second.stsz_Sample_Count=Sample_Count;
6249
6250 if (Sample_Count>1 && Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "BitRate_Mode").empty())
6251 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "BitRate_Mode", "CBR");
6252
6253 }
6254 else
6255 {
6256 int32u Size;
6257 /*
6258 if (FieldSize==4)
6259 BS_Begin(); //Too much slow
6260 */
6261 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<Sample_Count; Pos++)
6262 {
6263 //Too much slow
6264 /*
6265 switch(FieldSize)
6266 {
6267 case 4 : Get_S4 (4, Size, "Size"); break;
6268 case 8 : {int8u Size1; Get_B1 (Size1, "Size"); Size=Size1;} break;
6269 case 16 : {int16u Size2; Get_B2 (Size2, "Size"); Size=Size2;} break;
6270 case 32 : {int32u Size4; Get_B4 (Size4, "Size"); Size=Size4;} break;
6271 default : return;
6272 }
6273 */
6274
6275 //Faster
6276 if (Element_Offset+4>Element_Size)
6277 break; //Problem
6278 switch(FieldSize)
6279 {
6280 case 4 : if (Sample_Count%2)
6281 Size=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset]&0x0F;
6282 else
6283 {
6284 Size=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset]>>4;
6285 Element_Offset++;
6286 }
6287 break;
6288 case 8 : Size=BigEndian2int8u (Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset); Element_Offset++; break;
6289 case 16 : Size=BigEndian2int16u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset); Element_Offset+=2; break;
6290 case 32 : Size=BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset); Element_Offset+=4; break;
6291 default : return;
6292 }
6293
6294 Stream->second.stsz_StreamSize+=Size;
6295 Stream->second.stsz_Total.push_back(Size);
6296 if (Pos<FrameCount_MaxPerStream)
6297 Stream->second.stsz.push_back(Size);
6298 }
6299 /*
6300 if (FieldSize==4)
6301 BS_End(); //Too much slow
6302 */
6303 }
6304}
6305
6306//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6307void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stts()
6308{
6309 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Time to Sample");
6310
6311 //Parsing
6312 int32u NumberOfEntries;
6313 Get_B4(NumberOfEntries, "Number of entries");
6314
6315 Stream=Streams.find(moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID);
6316 Stream->second.stts_Min=(int32u)-1;
6317 Stream->second.stts_Max=0;
6318 Stream->second.stts_FrameCount=0;
6319 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6320 std::map<int32u, int64u> Duration_FrameCount; //key is duration
6321 int64u Duration_FrameCount_Max=0;
6322 int32u Duration_FrameCount_Max_Duration=0;
6323 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Video && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "Format")==__T("DV") && Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0] && ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts==NULL)
6324 ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts=new File_DvDif::stts;
6325 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6326
6327 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
6328 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stts_Durations.clear();
6329 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
6330
6331 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<NumberOfEntries; Pos++)
6332 {
6333 int32u SampleCount, SampleDuration;
6334 Get_B4(SampleCount, "Sample Count");
6335 Get_B4(SampleDuration, "Sample Duration");
6336
6337 moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stts_Common(SampleCount, SampleDuration, Pos, NumberOfEntries);
6338
6339 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6340 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Video && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "Format")==__T("DV"))
6341 {
6342 File_DvDif::stts_part DV_stts_Part;
6343 DV_stts_Part.Pos_Begin=Stream->second.stts_FrameCount-SampleCount;
6344 DV_stts_Part.Pos_End=Stream->second.stts_FrameCount;
6345 DV_stts_Part.Duration=SampleDuration;
6346 ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->push_back(DV_stts_Part);
6347
6348 Duration_FrameCount[SampleDuration]+=Stream->second.stts_FrameCount;
6349 if (Duration_FrameCount_Max<=Duration_FrameCount[SampleDuration])
6350 {
6351 Duration_FrameCount_Max=Duration_FrameCount[SampleDuration];
6352 Duration_FrameCount_Max_Duration=SampleDuration;
6353 }
6354 }
6355 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6356 }
6357
6358 FILLING_BEGIN();
6359 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Video)
6360 {
6361 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_FrameCount, Stream->second.stts_FrameCount);
6362
6363 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6364 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Video && Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, "Format")==__T("DV"))
6365 {
6366 //Clean up the "normal" value
6367 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->size(); Pos++)
6368 {
6369 if (((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->at(Pos).Duration==Duration_FrameCount_Max_Duration)
6370 {
6371 ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->erase(((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->begin()+Pos);
6372 Pos--;
6373 }
6374 }
6375
6376 if (((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts->empty())
6377 {delete ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts; ((File_DvDif*)Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Parsers[0])->Mpeg4_stts=NULL;}
6378 }
6379 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DVDIF_ANALYZE_YES
6380 }
6381 FILLING_END();
6382}
6383
6384void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_mdia_minf_stbl_stts_Common(int32u SampleCount, int32u SampleDuration, int32u Pos, int32u NumberOfEntries)
6385{
6386 FILLING_BEGIN();
6387 stream::stts_struct Stts;
6388 Stts.SampleCount=SampleCount;
6389 Stts.SampleDuration=SampleDuration;
6390 Stream->second.stts.push_back(Stts);
6391 if (Pos==1 && NumberOfEntries>=2 && NumberOfEntries<=3 && Stream->second.stts_FrameCount==1 && Stts.SampleDuration!=Stream->second.stts_Max && Stream->second.mdhd_TimeScale)
6392 {
6393 Stream->second.stts_Duration_FirstFrame=Stream->second.stts[0].SampleDuration;
6394 Stream->second.stts_Min=Stts.SampleDuration;
6395 Stream->second.stts_Max=Stts.SampleDuration;
6396 }
6397 if (NumberOfEntries>=2 && NumberOfEntries<=3 && Pos+1==NumberOfEntries && Stts.SampleCount==1 && Stream->second.stts_Min==Stream->second.stts_Max && Stts.SampleDuration!=Stream->second.stts_Max && Stream->second.mdhd_TimeScale)
6398 {
6399 Stream->second.stts_Duration_LastFrame=Stts.SampleDuration;
6400 }
6401 else
6402 {
6403 if (Stts.SampleDuration<Stream->second.stts_Min) Stream->second.stts_Min=Stts.SampleDuration;
6404 if (Stts.SampleDuration>Stream->second.stts_Max) Stream->second.stts_Max=Stts.SampleDuration;
6405 }
6406 Stream->second.stts_FrameCount+=Stts.SampleCount;
6407 if (Stts.SampleDuration<0x80000000)
6408 Stream->second.stts_Duration+=Stts.SampleCount*Stts.SampleDuration;
6409 else
6410 Stream->second.stts_Duration-=Stts.SampleCount*(((int32u)-1)-Stts.SampleDuration+1); //Negative value
6411
6412 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
6413 stream::stts_duration stts_Duration;
6414 stts_Duration.Pos_Begin=Stream->second.stts_FrameCount-Stts.SampleCount;
6415 stts_Duration.Pos_End=Stream->second.stts_FrameCount;
6416 stts_Duration.SampleDuration=Stts.SampleDuration;
6417 if (Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stts_Durations.empty())
6418 stts_Duration.DTS_Begin=0;
6419 else
6420 {
6421 stream::stts_durations::iterator Previous=Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stts_Durations.end(); --Previous;
6422 stts_Duration.DTS_Begin=Previous->DTS_End;
6423 }
6424 stts_Duration.DTS_End=stts_Duration.DTS_Begin+Stts.SampleCount*Stts.SampleDuration;
6425 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].stts_Durations.push_back(stts_Duration);
6426 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
6427 FILLING_END();
6428}

6466//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6467void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_tkhd()
6468{
6469 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Track Header")
6470
6471 //Parsing
6472 Ztring Date_Created, Date_Modified;
6473 float32 a, b, u, c, d, v, x, y, w;
6474 int64u Duration;
6475 int16u Volume, Alternate_Group;
6476 bool Enabled;
6477 Get_Flags(Flags, 0, Enabled, "Track Enabled");
6478 Skip_Flags(Flags, 1, "Track in Movie");
6479 Skip_Flags(Flags, 2, "Track in Preview");
6480 Skip_Flags(Flags, 3, "Track in Poster");
6481 Get_DATE1904_DEPENDOFVERSION(Date_Created, "Creation time");
6482 Get_DATE1904_DEPENDOFVERSION(Date_Modified, "Modification time");
6483 Get_B4 (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID, "Track ID"); Element_Info1(moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID);
6484 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
6485 Get_B_DEPENDOFVERSION(Duration, "Duration"); if (moov_mvhd_TimeScale) {Param_Info2(Duration*1000/moov_mvhd_TimeScale, " ms"); Element_Info2(Duration*1000/moov_mvhd_TimeScale, " ms");}
6486 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
6487 Skip_B4( "Reserved");
6488 Skip_B2( "Layer");
6489 Get_B2(Alternate_Group, "Alternate group");
6490 Get_B2 (Volume, "Volume"); Param_Info1(Ztring::ToZtring(((float)Volume)/256));
6491 Skip_B2( "Reserved");
6492 Element_Begin1("Matrix structure");
6493 Get_BFP4(16, a, "a (width scale)");
6494 Get_BFP4(16, b, "b (width rotate)");
6495 Get_BFP4( 2, u, "u (width angle)");
6496 Get_BFP4(16, c, "c (height rotate)");
6497 Get_BFP4(16, d, "d (height scale)");
6498 Get_BFP4( 2, v, "v (height angle)");
6499 Get_BFP4(16, x, "x (position left)");
6500 Get_BFP4(16, y, "y (position top)");
6501 Get_BFP4( 2, w, "w (divider)");
6502 Element_End0();
6503 Get_BFP4(16, moov_trak_tkhd_Width, "Track width");
6504 Get_BFP4(16, moov_trak_tkhd_Height, "Track height");
6505
6506 FILLING_BEGIN();
6507 //Case of header is after main part
6508 std::map<int32u, stream>::iterator Temp=Streams.find((int32u)-1);
6509 if (Temp!=Streams.end())
6510 {
6511 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID]=Temp->second;
6512 Temp->second.Parsers.clear(); //They are a copy, we don't want that the destructor deletes the Parser
6513 Streams.erase(Temp);
6514 }
6515 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].IsEnabled = Enabled;
6516 if (Alternate_Group) Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "AlternateGroup", Alternate_Group);
6517 if (moov_mvhd_TimeScale)
6518 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "Duration", float64_int64s(((float64)Duration)*1000/moov_mvhd_TimeScale));
6519 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "Encoded_Date", Date_Created);
6520 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, "Tagged_Date", Date_Modified);
6521 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_ID, moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID, 10, true);
6522 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].tkhd_Duration=Duration;
6523 if (moov_trak_tkhd_Height*d)
6524 moov_trak_tkhd_DisplayAspectRatio=(moov_trak_tkhd_Width*a)/(moov_trak_tkhd_Height*d);
6525 moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation=(float32)(std::atan2(b, a)*180.0/3.14159);
6526 if (moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation<0)
6527 moov_trak_tkhd_Rotation+=360;
6528
6529 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
6530 if (StreamIDs_Size>1 && Config->File_ID_OnlyRoot_Get())
6531 StreamIDs_Width[StreamIDs_Size-1]=Streams.size()<=1?0:8; //If referenced file and more than 1 stream, referenced ID is discarded, else referenced ID is used
6532 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
6533 FILLING_END();
6534}
6535void File_Mpeg4::moov_trak_txas()
6536{
6537 Element_Name("Track Exclude");

6747//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6748void File_Mpeg4::moov_udta_chpl()
6749{
6750 Element_Name("Chapters");
6751
6752 //Parsing
6753 Ztring Value;
6754 std::string ValueS;
6755 int64u Time;
6756 int8u Size;
6757 size_t Pos=0;
6758 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Menu);
6759 Skip_B8( "Unknown");
6760 Skip_B1( "Chapter Count");
6761 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Chapters_Pos_Begin, Count_Get(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last), 10, true);
6762 while (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
6763 {
6764 Get_B8 (Time, "Time");
6765 Get_B1 (Size, "Text size");
6766 Get_String(Size, ValueS, "Value");
6767 Value.From_UTF8(ValueS.c_str());
6768 if (Value.empty())
6769 Value.From_Local(ValueS.c_str()); //Trying Local...
6770
6771 FILLING_BEGIN();
6772 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(Time/10000).To_Local().c_str(), Value);
6773 FILLING_END();
6774
6775 //Next
6776 Pos++;
6777 }
6778 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Chapters_Pos_End, Count_Get(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last), 10, true);
6779}
6780
6781//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
6782void File_Mpeg4::moov_udta_clsf()
6783{
6784 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Classification"); //3GP
6785
6786 //Parsing
6787 Ztring ClassificationInfo;
6788 int32u ClassificationEntity;
6789 int16u Language, ClassificationTable;
6790 Get_C4(ClassificationEntity, "ClassificationEntity");
6791 Get_C2(ClassificationTable, "ClassificationTable");
6792 Get_B2(Language, "Language");
6793 bool Utf8=true;
6794 if (Element_Offset+2<=Element_Size)
6795 {
6796 int16u Utf16;
6797 Peek_B2(Utf16);
6798 if (Utf16==0xFEFF)
6799 Utf8=false;
6800 }
6801 if (Utf8)
6802 Get_UTF8(Element_Size-Element_Offset, ClassificationInfo, "ClassificationInfo");
6803 else
6804 Get_UTF16(Element_Size-Element_Offset, ClassificationInfo, "ClassificationInfo");
6805
6806 FILLING_BEGIN();
6807 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Classification", Ztring().From_CC4(ClassificationTable));
6808 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "Classification_Reason", ClassificationInfo);
6809 FILLING_END();
6810}

6931 Get_B1(KeywordCnt, "KeywordCnt");
6932 for (int8u Pos=0; Pos<KeywordCnt; Pos++)
6933 {
6934 Ztring KeywordInfo;
6935 int8u KeywordSize;
6936 Get_B1(KeywordSize, "KeywordSize");
6937 bool Utf8=true;
6938 if (Element_Offset+2<=Element_Size)
6939 {

6943 Utf8=false;
6944 }
6945 if (Utf8)
6946 Get_UTF8(KeywordSize, KeywordInfo, "KeywordInfo");
6947 else
6948 Get_UTF16(KeywordSize, KeywordInfo, "KeywordInfo");
6949
6950 FILLING_BEGIN();

6952 FILLING_END();

7031//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
7032void File_Mpeg4::moov_udta_meta_uuid()
7033{
7034 int128u uuid;
7035 Get_UUID(uuid, "uuid");
7036 if (uuid.hi == 0x7C92A0DB249B5CA3LL && uuid.lo == 0x900807802D903119LL) // AtomicParsley imdb
7037 {
7038 int32u FourCC;
7039 Get_B4(FourCC, "4CC");
7040 if (FourCC == 0x696D6462) // "imdb"
7041 {
7042 int32u Type;
7043 Get_B4(Type, "Type");
7044 if (Type == 1) // UTF-8 text?
7045 {
7046 if (Element_Offset+4<=Element_Size)
7047 {
7048 Peek_B4(Type);
7049 if (!Type)
7050 Skip_B4( "Zeroes?");
7051 }
7052
7053 Ztring Value;
7054 Get_UTF8(Element_Size-Element_Offset, Value, "Value");
7055
7056 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "IMDb", Value);
7057 }
7058 else
7059 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Unknown");
7060 }
7061 else
7062 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Unknown");
7063 }
7064 else
7065 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Unknown");
7066}

7196//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
7197void File_Mpeg4::moov_udta_xxxx()
7198{
7199 //Getting the method
7200 std::string Parameter;
7201 method Method=Metadata_Get(Parameter, Element_Code);
7202 Element_Info1(Parameter.c_str());
7203
7204 if (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID!=(int32u)-1)
7205 switch (Method)
7206 {
7207 case Method_String:
7208 case Method_String2:
7209 Method=Method_String3; break;
7210 default: ;
7211 }
7212
7213 switch (Method)
7214 {
7215 case Method_None :
7216 {
7217 Element_Name("Unknown");
7218 }
7219 break;
7220 case Method_Binary :
7221 {
7222 Element_Name("Binary");
7223 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown");
7224 return;
7225 }
7226 break;
7227 case Method_String :
7228 {
7229 Element_Name("Text");
7230
7231 //Parsing
7232 Ztring Value;
7233 int32u Size32=0;
7234 int16u Size16=0, Language;
7235 bool IsText=true;
7236 if (Element_Size<=4)
7237 IsText=false;
7238 else
7239 {
7240 Peek_B4(Size32);
7241 if (4+(int64u)Size32>Element_Size)
7242 {
7243 Size32=0;
7244 Peek_B2(Size16);
7245 if (4+(int64u)Size16>Element_Size)
7246 IsText=false;
7247 }
7248 }
7249 if (!IsText)
7250 {
7251 Skip_XX(Element_Size, "Unknown");
7252 return;
7253 }
7254
7255 while(Element_Offset<Element_Size)
7256 {
7257 if (Size32)
7258 {
7259 Get_Local(Size32, Value, "Value");
7260 Get_B4 (Size32, "Size");
7261 }
7262 else
7263 {
7264 Get_B2 (Size16, "Size");
7265 Get_B2 (Language, "Language"); Param_Info1(Language_Get(Language));
7266 Get_Local(Size16, Value, "Value");
7267 }
7268
7269 FILLING_BEGIN();
7270 if (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID==(int32u)-1)
7271 {
7272 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str()).empty())
7273 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str(), Value);
7274 }
7275 else
7276 {
7277 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Infos[Parameter]=Value;
7278 }
7279 FILLING_END();
7280
7281 if (Element_Offset+1==Element_Size)
7282 {
7283 int8u Null;
7284 Peek_B1(Null);
7285 if (Null==0x00)
7286 Skip_B1( "NULL");
7287 }
7288 if (Element_Offset+4<=Element_Size && Size32)
7289 {
7290 int32u Null;
7291 Peek_B4(Null);
7292 if (Null==0x00000000)
7293 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset,"Padding");
7294 }
7295 if (Element_Offset+2<=Element_Size && Size16)
7296 {
7297 int16u Null;
7298 Peek_B2(Null);
7299 if (Null==0x0000)
7300 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset,"Padding");
7301 }
7302 }
7303 }
7304 break;
7305 case Method_String2 :
7306 {
7307 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Text");
7308
7309 //Parsing
7310 Ztring Value;
7311 int16u Language;
7312 while(Element_Offset<Element_Size)
7313 {
7314 Get_B2(Language, "Language"); Param_Info1(Language_Get(Language));
7315 bool Utf8=true;
7316 if (Element_Offset+2<=Element_Size)
7317 {
7318 int16u Utf16;
7319 Peek_B2(Utf16);
7320 if (Utf16==0xFEFF)
7321 Utf8=false;
7322 }
7323 if (Utf8)
7324 Get_UTF8(Element_Size-Element_Offset, Value, "Value");
7325 else
7326 Get_UTF16(Element_Size-Element_Offset, Value, "Value");
7327
7328 FILLING_BEGIN();
7329 if (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID==(int32u)-1)
7330 {
7331 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str()).empty())
7332 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str(), Value);
7333 }
7334 else
7335 {
7336 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Infos[Parameter]=Value;
7337 }
7338 FILLING_END();
7339 }
7340 }
7341 break;
7342 case Method_String3 :
7343 {
7344 if (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID==(int32u)-1)
7345 {
7346 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Text");
7347 }
7348
7349 //Parsing
7350 Ztring Value;
7351 while(Element_Offset<Element_Size)
7352 {
7353 Get_UTF8(Element_Size-Element_Offset, Value,"Value");
7354
7355 FILLING_BEGIN();
7356 if (moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID==(int32u)-1)
7357 {
7358 if (Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str()).empty())
7359 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Parameter.c_str(), Value);
7360 }
7361 else
7362 {
7363 if (Parameter!="Omud" // Some complex data is in Omud, but nothing interessant found
7364 && Parameter!="_SGI" // Found "_SGIxV4" with DM_IMAGE_PIXEL_ASPECT, in RLE, ignoring it for the moment
7365 && Parameter!="hway") // Unknown
7366 Streams[moov_trak_tkhd_TrackID].Infos[Parameter]=Value;
7367 }
7368 FILLING_END();
7369 }
7370 }
7371 break;
7372 case Method_Integer :
7373 {
7374 Element_Name("Integer");
7375
7376 //Parsing
7377 Skip_XX(4, "Value");
7378 }
7379 break;
7380 }
7381}
7382
7383//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
7384void File_Mpeg4::pdin()
7385{
7386 NAME_VERSION_FLAG("Progressive Download Information");
7387
7388 //Parsing
7389 while (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
7390 {
7391 Skip_B4( "Rate");
7392 Skip_B4( "Initial Delay");
7393 }
7394}

7412

7414 Accept("QTCA");
7415
7416 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format, "MPEG-4");
7417 CodecID_Fill(__T("QTCA"), Stream_General, 0, InfoCodecID_Format_Mpeg4);
7418 FILLING_END();
7419}
